set_id: if(B2, query(sets!$A:$B, "select A where (B='"&A2&"' or B like '%:"&A2&":%' or B like '"&A2&":%' or B like '%:"&A2&"') limit 1", 0))
show_id: if(G2, query(shows!$A:$I, "select A where (D="&G2&" or E="&G2&" or F="&G2&" or G="&G2&" or H="&G2&" or I="&G2&")", 0))
next_perfid: if(and(B2,H2), query(A$2:H, "select (A) where (B = "&B2&" and H > "&H2&") order by H asc limit 1", 0))
